description: I really want to thank each and every one of my fans. The positive response to the comics I found have blown me away. I can't wait to start uploading these comics periodically over time for you eyes to enjoy. It will be so fun seeing you guys theorizing what will happen in the future chapters to come. It's almost like this is my own personal, official tv show. Just one step closer to bringing back Sonic Underground, bitches.
